===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#A [[design]] that may be read as the same word or phrase (or sometimes two different words or phrases) when [[orient]]ed in two different ways, usually when [[reflect]]ed in a vertical [[axis]] or when [[rotate]]d through 180 [[degree]]s.

